```
# Julia installation directories
julia-*/
julia.tar.gz

# Compiled Julia files
*.ji
*.so

# Julia cache and compiled files
**/compiled/
**/base.cache

# Julia config files
**/julia-config.jl

# Julia appdata
**/appdata/

# Julia stdlib artifacts and test packages
**/StdlibArtifacts.toml
**/Artifacts.toml
**/test_packages/
**/depot/

# Julia build/test related
**/build.jl
**/Manifest.toml

# Julia extensions and generated files
**/ext/
**/gen/

# Julia documentation build files
**/docs/build/
**/docs/Project.toml

# Julia test related
**/test/
**/runtests.jl

# Julia package related
**/Pkg/test/
**/Pkg/ext/

# Julia registry and package cache
**/.pkg/
**/registries/
**/packages/

# Julia REPL and history
**/.julia/
**/repl_history.jl

# Julia coverage
**/.coverage
**/coverage/

# Julia specific temp files
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/tmp/
```